{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act19side_level_act19side_07_end","storyGroup":"act19side","storySort":17,"storyDependence":"act19side_level_act19side_07_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"DV-7","storyName":"疯狂的信号","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"在莱茵总部，博士与塞雷娅找到了失联多日的总辖。\n分别多年后，曾经的老友终于重逢。\n","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act19side/level_act19side_07_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act19side_07","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":15,"next":17,"characters":["莱茵实验员","缪尔赛思","塞雷娅","？？？","帕尔维斯","霍尔海雅","Mechanist","玛丽","埃琳娜","莱茵防卫科成员","桑尼","斐尔迪南","哥伦比亚雇佣兵"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"Dialog","id":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":2},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":3},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g9_headquarter","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_530_1#1$1","id":7},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵实验员","text":"咦，这不是缪尔赛思主任吗？这么晚了您还来公司啊。","id":8},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#6","id":9},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"呃......咳咳，是啊，有工作没干完。","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_530_1#1$1","id":11},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵实验员","text":"您可真是辛苦啊。","id":12},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_530_1#1$1","id":13},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵实验员","text":"这两位是？","id":14},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#8$1","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......","id":16},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"......我们的重要合作伙伴。","id":18},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"你没认出这位吗？","id":19},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_530_1#1$1","id":20},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵实验员","text":"呃......我看不清脸......","id":21},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#6","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"这位可是源石理论学者、矿石病专家、天灾研究者，大名鼎鼎的——","id":23},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_530_1#1$1","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵实验员","text":"原来是您啊！真是难得的机会，竟然让我碰到了像您这么厉害的科学家！","id":25},{"type":"character","id":26},{"type":"dialog","id":27},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"29","text":"（他根本没听说过我吧？）"},{"id":"29","text":"......"},{"id":"29","text":"（这都能糊弄过去？）"}],"values":[],"id":28},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":29,"end":41},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#6","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"我们有急事需要尽快上楼——有机会的话，下回一起开午餐会啊。","id":31},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_530_1#1$1","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵实验员","text":"当然。那就不耽误您的时间了......","id":33},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......","id":35},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_530_1#1$1","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵实验员","text":"等一下，我刚才就觉得您很眼熟，您难道不是那位防......防......","id":37},{"type":"character","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......防护材料领域非常有名的专家。","id":39},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#5$1","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"帕尔维斯......","id":41,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":42},{"type":"character","id":43},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":44},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":45},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"这几年莱茵的扩张速度很快，不是吗？","id":47},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","id":48},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"新来的小朋友们还需要多长长见识啊。","id":49},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_530_1#1$1","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵实验员","text":"......两位主任同时出现？我、我......我还有工作没做完！我先走啦！","id":51},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"呵呵。","id":53},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#6$1","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......你不准备告诉他们我回来了吗？","id":55},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","id":56},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"请原谅我的老花眼，我以前认识您吗，美丽的瓦伊凡女士？","id":57},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":58},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......","id":59},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","id":60},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"没什么事情的话，我就先回去了。太晚休息可不利于我这把年纪的人的身体健康。","id":61},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"对了，缪尔赛思主任，别忘了你答应我的黑豆茶。","id":63},{"type":"dialog","id":64},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":65},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":66},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":67},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#4","id":68},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"呼......他真的是路过吗，塞雷娅？","id":69},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":70},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"现在是凌晨四点。","id":71},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#9$1","id":72},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"帕尔维斯平常的下班时间是九个小时以前。","id":73},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#4","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"果然......直到最后一刻到来前，他都不会轻易把赌注压在斐尔迪南和克丽斯腾之间的任意一方身上。","id":75},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#4","id":76},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"他还想看看谁的赢面大呢。","id":77},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#4","id":78},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"就算莱茵生命变成了废墟，他也一定是能活下来的那个吧？","id":79},{"type":"Dialog","id":80},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":81},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":82},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g7_mainstreet_n","screenadapt":"coverall","id":83},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":84},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"......他们进了莱茵总部。","id":86},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":87},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"领航小队，准备拦截。","id":88},{"type":"dialog","id":89},{"type":"character","id":90},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":91},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"别着急。","id":93},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#2$1","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"你是......","id":95},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":96},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"我见过你和塞雷娅交手，对你的装备很感兴趣。","id":97},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":98},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"方便借我看一眼吗？","id":99},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":100},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"......","id":101},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#2$1","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"在战斗之前，你们是这么打招呼的吗，罗德岛的精英干员？","id":103},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"请不要误解，刚才那句话，我不是以罗德岛精英干员的身份说的。","id":105},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":106},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"作为一名机械师，我尊重任何优秀的技术及技术的发明者——","id":107},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"所以，在我夺下你那根形制特别的法杖之前，我想先询问一下你的意愿。","id":109},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":110},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"......你很有趣，Mechanist先生。","id":111},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"我之前只是想去见一见塞雷娅，但你和你的上司......那位博士给了我更大的惊喜。","id":113},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":114},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"你知道我的名字？","id":115},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#10$1","id":116},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"你也调查过我，不是吗？","id":117},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#10$1","id":118},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"掌握尽量多的信息，是我们这类人在动手之前的习惯。","id":119},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"......莱茵总部的资料库里有你的名字，霍尔海雅女士。","id":121},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":122},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"但我不相信斐尔迪南会雇佣一名历史学家来追杀自己的同僚。就算是在充满不可能的哥伦比亚学界，这也太荒诞了。","id":123},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"那只是我的副业。","id":125},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":126},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"你的副业是研究历史？","id":127},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#9$1","id":128},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"错了。","id":129},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":130},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"我是一名历史学者，我在这里，只是为了见证一则流传千年的预言成真。","id":131},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":132},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"同样的，我也相信，未来的走向能揭示一些被掩埋的历史——","id":133},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":134},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"我和你们一样，都是真相的追寻者。","id":135},{"type":"Dialog","id":136},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":137},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":138},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":139},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g2_edgeofbase","screenadapt":"coverall","id":140},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":141},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$exciting_intro","key":"$exciting_loop","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":142,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":143},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"我们到了。","id":145},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"知道怎么去找你的混蛋上司吗，研究员小姐？","id":147},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":148},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"他应该在监控室里。","id":149},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"拐角的地方有个通风口，要是能爬上去的话，就能用最快的速度抵达监控室。","id":151},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":152},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"动作要快。","id":153},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"毕竟，很快就有很多人来迎接我们了。","id":155},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":156},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"......警长。","id":157},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":158},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"我就知道你会站到对面去。你的意志还是不够坚定，你忘不了你和这名罪犯的过去。","id":159},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"他还不是罪犯，小子，能定罪的人从来不是你们。","id":161},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"......你在走一条不归路。","id":163},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"为什么？你们明明都那么优秀，为什么要自毁前程？为什么......她也不听我的劝阻？","id":165},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"你真正想提问的对象并不是我，对吧？","id":167},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":168},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"但我也可以替她再教你一回。","id":169},{"type":"dialog","id":170},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":171},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":172},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_arrowshot","volume":"1","id":173},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","volume":"1","id":174},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":175},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":176},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":177},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$swordtsing1","volume":"1","id":178},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.4","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"呃——","id":180},{"type":"dialog","id":181},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"因为我们知道自己战斗是为了什么。","id":183},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"为了守护某些人......守护某些准则不被像那个混蛋主任那样的人践踏，我们从来不会犹豫。","id":185},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"我们不会像你一样......","id":187},{"type":"dialog","id":188},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":189},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":190},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_arrowshot","volume":"1","id":191},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","volume":"1","id":192},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":193},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":194},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"落脚之前总是先看好阵营——","id":196},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#5$1","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"动手之前还要问为什么！","id":198},{"type":"dialog","id":199},{"type":"character","id":200},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":201},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":202},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"1","text":"","id":203},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":204},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":205},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":206},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"唔......！","id":207},{"type":"dialog","id":208},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","id":209},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","id":210},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.7","id":211},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":212},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","volume":"0.8","id":213},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":214},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":215},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_attack_ready","volume":"0.8","id":216},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":217},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"你们找到方向了吗？","id":219},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":220},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"我想是的......","id":221},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"那快走吧。","id":223},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你呢？","id":225},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":226},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"我有弩，你没有。所以先别管我了，管好你自己。","id":227},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#10$1","id":228},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"......谢谢。","id":229},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":230},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"保重。","id":231},{"type":"dialog","id":232},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.5","id":233},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":234},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":235},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":236},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......","id":237},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":238},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"你怎么不跟上去？你一路走到这里，不也是为了找那家伙算账吗？","id":239},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......我也有武器。","id":241},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":242},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"嗯？","id":243},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我们很久没有并肩作战了，玛丽。","id":245},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":246},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"什么并肩作战......那时候只是玩游戏。","id":247},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":248},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"再说了，哪一次游戏不是我带你？","id":249},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":250},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"哈哈......谢谢。","id":251},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":252},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我真的很想念......很想念那段时光。","id":253},{"type":"dialog","id":254},{"type":"character","id":255},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":256},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":257},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_arrowshot","volume":"1","id":258},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","volume":"1","id":259},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":260},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":261},{"type":"Dialog","id":262},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":263},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":264},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":265},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g9_headquarter","screenadapt":"coverall","id":266},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":267},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":268,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#4","id":269},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"只要从前面的电梯上去，就能直达总辖办公室。","id":270},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#8$1","id":271},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"走后面的安全通道会是更保险的做法。","id":272},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","id":273},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"我知道啊，可我们不是在赶时间吗？","id":274},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","id":275},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"直接走的话肯定更快，要应对的武装人员也能更少些......","id":276},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#4$1","id":277},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"等等，别走到前面那个位置——","id":278},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","id":279},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"咦？","id":281},{"type":"dialog","id":282},{"type":"character","id":283},{"type":"dialog","id":284},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$alarmenter","channel":"bgs","volume":"1","block":"false","loop":"true","id":285},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.4","r":"255","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":286},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":287},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.4","r":"255","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":288},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":289},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":290},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":291},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#3$1","id":292},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......","id":293},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#2","id":294},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"抱歉，我忘了，那里是监控区......","id":295},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":296},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"博士，我们要转备用计划了。","id":297},{"type":"dialog","id":298},{"type":"character","id":299},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$batmeeting_intro","key":"$batmeeting_loop","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":300,"musicid":3},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","volume":"0.8","id":301},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":302},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":303},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"发现入侵者！","id":304},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"这里，在这里！","id":305},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"抓住这几个入侵——等等，主任？","id":307},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#8$1","id":308},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"你好，雷吉。","id":309},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":310},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"......","id":311},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":312},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"您怎么回来了......不，您已经没有权限，不能再往前走了......","id":313},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#8$1","id":314},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"面对入侵者，展露出内心的犹豫只会给敌人机会。","id":315},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#4$1","id":316},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"需要我再教你一遍该怎么做吗？","id":317},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":318},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"......举盾！","id":319},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":320},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"眩晕器准备，瞄准入侵者——塞雷娅！","id":321},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#3$1","id":322},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"勉强算你合格。","id":323},{"type":"dialog","id":324},{"type":"character","id":325},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":326},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":327},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"1","text":"","id":328},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":329},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":330},{"type":"Dialog","id":331},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":332},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":333},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":334},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g11_monitoringroom","screenadapt":"coverall","id":335},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":336},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":337,"musicid":4},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":338},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"最新一批数据都记录好了吗？","id":339},{"type":"character","id":340},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"好了。","id":341},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":342},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"注意无人机的方位。","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"不要让实验体的行动影响到第一手数据的采集。","id":344},{"type":"character","id":345},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"放心，老板。","id":346},{"type":"dialog","id":347},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.5","id":348},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","fadetime":"1","id":349},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":350},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你想要的第一手数据已经自己走到你面前来了。","id":351},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":352},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......","id":353},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":354},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"埃琳娜。","id":355},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":356},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我很高兴......你没事。","id":357},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":358},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"我在你手下工作了那么多年，阅读你的微表情也变成了工作的一部分——","id":359},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你的左侧眉毛轻微地上挑了一下。你明明很惊讶，老板。","id":360},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":361},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......你总是能给我很多惊喜。","id":362},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":363},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"你回来了，我终于可以好好松口气——那些蠢笨的新人需要像你这么优秀的研究员好好调教。","id":364},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":365},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你想让我当组长？","id":366},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#2$1","id":367},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"不，不是组长。","id":368},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":369},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"看到桌上那把钥匙了吗？收下它。","id":370},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":371},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"你已经完全证明了自己的能力。你不再需要给任何人——无论是我还是多萝西——当助手。","id":372},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":373},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"下一个项目，你会是第一负责人。","id":374},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":375},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"这把钥匙就是我为你准备好的礼物。那是一间崭新的......空间充裕的实验室，属于你的实验室。","id":376},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":377},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"无论你想做什么研究，我和莱茵生命都会全力支持你。","id":378},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#1$1","id":379},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"太棒了。","id":380},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#1$1","id":381},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你是不是还考虑过让我接任能量科主任？","id":382},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#2$1","id":383},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......不是没有这种可能性。","id":384},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#1$1","id":385},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"......","id":386},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#7$1","id":387},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"你......你看起来并不惊喜。","id":388},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":389},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"因为无论你给我的未来规划了什么道路......我的答案都是“不”。","id":390},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#3$1","id":391},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......放下你的法杖。","id":392},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":393},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你在害怕什么？你怕我背叛你，在这个你即将迎来重大成功的关键时刻，让你没法看到自己的光辉未来？","id":394},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":395},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"或许我真的会考虑这么做。","id":396},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1","id":397},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我不明白。我明明给了你那么多......","id":398},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1","id":399},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我在你身上看到了天赋、勤勉和野心。","id":400},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1","id":401},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"这些都是取得成功的必要品质，也正是这些品质铸就了我自己。","id":402},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":403},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你当然不明白。","id":404},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":405},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"要是你真如你所言的那样器重我的话——你就应该把整个实验的真相都告诉我。","id":406},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":407},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"告诉我，你会无视那些受试者的安危，你会把我当成监视多萝西的工具，等没用的时候，就让我连同你罪恶的证据一起灰飞烟灭......","id":408},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":409},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"......在你眼中，我是不是一个特别听话的傻子？","id":410},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#6$1","id":411},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"奥利维亚明明提醒过我，我却直到你动手的最后一刻才醒悟过来！","id":412},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":413},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"你还没有准备好，埃琳娜，我怕你会动摇，就跟现在这样......","id":414},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":415},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你从来没有信任过我。","id":416},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":417},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你不相信任何人。斐尔迪南，你只信你自己。","id":418},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":419},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"那么，我凭什么要再信任你......相信你的这些许诺？","id":420},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":421},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我从来没有给过任何人那么多机会。","id":422},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#3$1","id":423},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"埃琳娜，你知道吗？你比我的孩子更像我。","id":424},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#3$1","id":425},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我在你身上倾注了那么多心血，即使此刻，只要你愿意，我依然允许你回到我身边——","id":426},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":427},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"......","id":428},{"type":"dialog","id":429},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":430},{"type":"Character","id":431},{"type":"Background","id":432},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":433},{"type":"Image","image":"29_i08","fadetime":"0","id":434},{"type":"ImageTween","xFrom":"-100","xTo":"0","yFrom":"-60","yTo":"0","duration":"60","xScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"0.9","yScaleFrom":"1","yScaleTo":"0.9","block":"false","id":435},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":436},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":437},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"就当我求你最后一件事——","id":438},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"闭嘴吧，老板。","id":439},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"带着你的“礼物”和这些虚情假意，离我远一点。","id":440},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"我，埃琳娜·乌比卡，从今天开始，不再是在你手下任你摆布的傻助手。","id":441},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"斐尔迪南·克鲁尼，你被我开除了。","id":442},{"type":"Dialog","id":443},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":444},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":445},{"type":"Image","id":446},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g11_monitoringroom","screenadapt":"coverall","id":447},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":448},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":449},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":450},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"......斐尔迪南主任！","id":451},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":452},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"给我抓住她，抓住这个暴徒！","id":453},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":454},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":455},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":456},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"唔......","id":457},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":458},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"主任，您没事吧？","id":459},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":460},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我没事。","id":461},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":462},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"埃琳娜......","id":463},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":464},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"不要......再用这种......看起来很关心我的眼神......看着我。","id":465},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":466},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"这让我觉得......恶心。","id":467},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":468},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......你说我不理解你，可你也并没有真正理解我。","id":469},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":470},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"也许......在刚才那一刹那，我是有过犹豫和担心。","id":471},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":472},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"那并不是我担心你给我捣乱，而是我在担心你。","id":473},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":474},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我是......真的不想看着你走到这一步。","id":475},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":476},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"这句话......","id":477},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":478},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"咳咳......我也想原样送给你。","id":479},{"type":"dialog","id":480},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":481},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1.5","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"20","randomness":"40","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":482},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_activation","volume":"1","id":483},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":484},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":485},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":486},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":487},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_magic_n","volume":"1","id":488},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_magic_m","volume":"1","id":489},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_atk_elecball_n","volume":"1","id":490},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$flashback","volume":"1","id":491},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","volume":"0.2","id":492},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":493},{"type":"Delay","time":"3","id":494},{"type":"Dialog","id":495},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":496},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":497},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g9_headquarter","screenadapt":"coverall","id":498},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":499},{"type":"dialog","id":500},{"type":"character","id":501},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","volume":"0.8","id":502},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":503},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":504},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","id":505},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"呼......呼......怎么办，防卫科的人越来越多了啊......","id":506},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","id":507},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"斐尔迪南还真是做足了准备，塞雷娅再能打，也很难一下子打退这么多人吧？","id":508},{"type":"dialog","id":509},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","focus":"-1","id":510},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"512","text":"还得麻烦你帮忙了，缪尔赛思主任。"}],"values":[],"id":511},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":512,"end":518},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","id":513},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"......我？不行的，我并不会打架啊。","id":514},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","id":515},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"光是跑来跑去躲避他们的攻击，我就已经很费劲了啊......","id":516},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","id":517},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"你没听到我呼呼喘气吗，博士？","id":518,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":519},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","focus":"-1","id":520},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"522","text":"你刚才就很巧妙地帮了塞雷娅一把，不是吗？"},{"id":"522","text":"只要你不再故意拖时间就行。"}],"values":[],"id":521},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":522,"end":524},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","id":523},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"你......你发现了？","id":524,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":525},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","focus":"-1","id":526},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"528","text":"塞雷娅很久没回莱茵总部，但还记得哪里是监控区。"},{"id":"528","text":"你总是有意无意干扰塞雷娅的视线。"}],"values":[],"id":527},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":528,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":529},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"531","text":"自从听到我猜测总辖就在这里，你明显不再着急。"}],"values":[],"id":530},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":531,"end":533},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","id":532},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"我......哎呀！","id":533,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":534},{"type":"character","id":535},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"0.6","id":536},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":537},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":538},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#2","id":539},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"......差一点就真的中招了啊。","id":540},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","id":541},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"博士......你竟然还拉着我？你......你还愿意拉着我吗？","id":542},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","id":543},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"明明猜到我可能有其他想法......","id":544},{"type":"dialog","id":545},{"type":"character","id":546},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"548","text":"有什么想法都是你的自由。"},{"id":"548","text":"我并不在乎你究竟是什么立场。"}],"values":[],"id":547},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":548,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":549},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"551","text":"我请你帮助塞雷娅。"}],"values":[],"id":550},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":551,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":552},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"554","text":"这是为了罗德岛和莱茵生命的共同利益。"},{"id":"554","text":"这是为了哥伦比亚与其他国家的安全考虑。"},{"id":"554","text":"这也是为了你。"}],"values":[],"id":553},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":554},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":555},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"......算上这次，你已经救了我两回了，Dr.{@nickname}。","id":556},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":557},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"好吧。","id":558},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":559},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"就当作是报答好了，至少这一回，我会站在你们身边，帮助塞雷娅去她想去的地方。","id":560},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#7","id":561},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"——","id":562},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#7","id":563},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"听到我的呼唤了吗，水分子？","id":564},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#7","id":565},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"亲吻眼前的每一位生灵，卷走脚下的所有尘埃吧！","id":566},{"type":"Dialog","id":567},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":568},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":569},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g7_mainstreet_n","screenadapt":"coverall","id":570},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":571},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":572},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"......精灵动摇了。","id":573},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":574},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"真是可怜的生灵......她总是希望自己能从其他人口中得到一些关于明天的允诺。","id":575},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":576},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"谁又会甘愿承认自己与自己所属的族群只属于过去呢？","id":577},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":578},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"克丽斯腾没法给她的东西，那位Dr.{@nickname}难道可以？","id":579},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","id":580},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"哥伦比亚雇佣兵","text":"女士，塞雷娅已经突破了封锁。","id":581,"figure":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":582},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"就让她见见自己的老朋友吧。","id":583,"figure":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":584},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"我还有其他工作要完成......只能下一次再与这位机械师先生交流了。","id":585,"figure":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#9$1","id":586},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"——要是他能从这批动力甲手中活下来的话。","id":587,"figure":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":588},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":589},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":590},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":591},{"type":"Text","text":"有多久没有回来了？","id":592},{"type":"Text","text":"一千四百九十七天。","id":593},{"type":"Text","text":"分别的时候，或许已是敌人。","id":594},{"type":"Text","text":"再见的时候，又还是朋友吗？","id":595},{"type":"Dialog","id":596},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":597},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g10_senioroffice","screenadapt":"coverall","id":598},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":599},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_537_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.7","fadetime":"2","id":600},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":601},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你回来了，塞雷娅。","id":602,"figure":"avg_npc_537_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":603},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......你好，克丽斯腾。","id":604,"figure":"avg_npc_537_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":605},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":606},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":607},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":608},{"type":"Character","id":609},{"type":"Image","id":610}],"characters":["莱茵实验员","缪尔赛思","塞雷娅","？？？","帕尔维斯","霍尔海雅","Mechanist","玛丽","埃琳娜","莱茵防卫科成员","桑尼","斐尔迪南","哥伦比亚雇佣兵"]}